&lt;p&gt;From README file:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;glob-strip is a standalone program designed to supply information to a pure data abstraction (information about files in the system, which can be used for managing playlists for example).&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;It is a gui socket server vritten in tcl Tk.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;tested on linux (Ubuntu 20.10) with tcl Tk 8.6 and pd (vanilla) 0.51.1&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;github: &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/marrongiallo/glob-strip&quot;&gt;glob-strip&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

