&lt;p&gt;shotcanvas is a Puredata plugin. This plugin is designed to use a PNG image as background of a pd patch. You can also create a PNG snapshot of your patch.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;tested on linux (Ubuntu 20.10) with tcl Tk 8.6 and pd (vanilla) 0.51.1&lt;/p&gt;

